residential.headline: INVEST...LIVE...BREATHE
residential.description:
This gorgeous 6 year old plantation built terrace house screams lifestyle. With no body corporate and stunning parkland views this home is ideal for new homeowners, an investor or anyone downsizing who still wants space.
Very generously designed over two levels, the internal layout offers four spacious bedrooms. They provide a multitude of features for comfortable living including built-in robes, ceiling fans and window treatments. With external access from two of these bedrooms, it only enhances the layout.
Upstairs, the long and spacious open plan kitchen/living/dining, with stylish timber flooring, also leads out to the external building, with views overlooking Edge Park. A split system reverse cycle air-conditioning keeps this home comfortable all year around. The functional galley style kitchen has a 900mm dual fuel cooker, range hood and Bosch dishwasher.
The modern, easily maintained bathrooms on each level cater for two bedrooms each. Upstairs on the living level the toilet is separate for ease when entertaining guests. Downstairs the modern bathroom features a bath for the ultimate relaxation.
The lower level also features an internal laundry with extra storage, tandem lockup garage with remote access, 3000L water tank and security screens throughout. The beautifully landscaped low maintenance lawn and gardens add a homely touch, without requiring your full attention every weekend.
There are no body corporate fees as this home is on its own title, with prime park side location and everything of need is within walking distance or a short drive. The local buses and schools are within walking distance, with Orion Shopping Centre being a 4 minute drive. This home is a must for any property portfolio.
